description: Called Orangehead jokingly by some of his friends, Kyousuke learns the tricks and trades of soccer from his illustrious elder brother, A.C. Milan playmaker Kanou Seisuke. After Seisuke`s departure, he slowly loses interest in the game, but rediscovers his love for it after a fated meeting with Miki. Initially joining as the coach of Joyou`s girl`s soccer team, the determination exhibited by the girls, especially Miki, invigorates his passion for soccer, and soon he joins Joyou`s male soccer team, emerging as their ace striker. In the last episode, he becomes a player for AFC Ajax.
name: Kanou Kyousuke
